---
import { Globe, MapPin, ArrowRight } from '@lucide/astro'
---

<section
  id='servicios'
  class='relative overflow-hidden py-24 md:py-32'
  style='scroll-margin-top: var(--navbar-height)'>

  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0'
    aria-hidden='true'
    class='dot-grid-28'>
  </div>

  <div class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-sage/20' aria-hidden='true'></div>
  <div class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-sage/10' aria-hidden='true'></div>

  <div class='relative mx-auto max-w-[860px] px-5'>

    <div class='mb-12'>
      <div data-animate class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-4'>
        <span class='block h-px w-10 bg-sage' aria-hidden='true'></span>
        <p class='text-sage'>Servicios SEO en Barcelona</p>
      </div>
      <p
        data-animate
        class='font-heading leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-base'>
        Elige la estrategia que necesita tu negocio<span class='text-sage'>.</span>
      </p>
      <div data-animate class='mt-5 flex items-center'>
        <div class='h-[3px] w-12 rounded-full bg-sage'></div>
        <div class='h-px w-20 bg-gradient-fade-end-sage'></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='flex flex-col gap-4'>

      <a
        href='/posicionamiento-web-barcelona/'
        data-animate
        class='group relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 bg-white border-surface-10 shadow-card'
        >

        <div class='pointer-events-none absolute left-0 top-0 h-full w-[3px] scale-y-0 origin-top rounded-r-full transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-y-100 bg-sage' aria-hidden='true'></div>

        <div class='relative overflow-hidden sm:w-[42%] shrink-0 px-6 py-7 flex flex-col justify-between gap-5 min-h-[160px] sm:min-h-0' bg-base>

          <svg class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 w-full h-full' aria-hidden='true' preserveAspectRatio='none'>
            <line x1='55%' y1='0%' x2='100%' y2='100%' stroke='rgba(250,234,177,0.08)' stroke-width='1' />
          </svg>

          <div
            class='pointer-events-none absolute -right-1 bottom-0 select-none leading-none'
            aria-hidden='true'
            class='font-heading text-cream-10 leading-none' style='font-size: 5.5rem;'>
            01
          </div>

          <div class='relative flex items-center gap-3'>
            <div class='flex size-9 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-sage/10 ring-1 ring-sage/30'>
              <Globe aria-hidden='true' class='size-4 text-sage' />
            </div>
            <span class='text-white-40'>Visibilidad en buscadores</span>
          </div>

          <div class='relative flex items-baseline gap-2'>
            <span class='leading-none tabular-nums shrink-0 text-cream-40'>01</span>
            <h2 class='text-base font-semibold tracking-tight leading-snug text-white'>Posicionamiento Web en Barcelona</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='flex flex-col justify-between gap-5 p-6 flex-1'>
          <p class='leading-relaxed text-base'>
            Aparece en Google cuando tus clientes buscan tus servicios. Auditoría técnica, contenidos orientados a captación y estrategia off page para que tu web trabaje por ti.
          </p>
          <div class='flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-sage'>
            Ver servicio
            <ArrowRight class='size-4 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-1.5' aria-hidden='true' />
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a
        href='/seo-local-barcelona/'
        data-animate
        class='group relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 bg-white border-surface-10 shadow-card'
        >

        <div class='pointer-events-none absolute left-0 top-0 h-full w-[3px] scale-y-0 origin-top rounded-r-full transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-y-100 bg-cream' aria-hidden='true'></div>

        <div class='relative overflow-hidden sm:w-[42%] shrink-0 px-6 py-7 flex flex-col justify-between gap-5 min-h-[160px] sm:min-h-0' bg-base>

          <svg class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 w-full h-full' aria-hidden='true' preserveAspectRatio='none'>
            <line x1='55%' y1='0%' x2='100%' y2='100%' stroke='rgba(250,234,177,0.08)' stroke-width='1' />
          </svg>

          <div
            class='pointer-events-none absolute -right-1 bottom-0 select-none leading-none'
            aria-hidden='true'
            class='font-heading text-cream-10 leading-none' style='font-size: 5.5rem;'>
            02
          </div>

          <div class='relative flex items-center gap-3'>
            <div class='flex size-9 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-cream/10 ring-1 ring-cream/30'>
              <MapPin aria-hidden='true' class='size-4 text-cream' />
            </div>
            <span class='text-white-40'>Visibilidad en Google Maps</span>
          </div>

          <div class='relative flex items-baseline gap-2'>
            <span class='leading-none tabular-nums shrink-0 text-cream-40'>02</span>
            <h2 class='text-base font-semibold tracking-tight leading-snug text-white'>SEO Local en Barcelona</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='flex flex-col justify-between gap-5 p-6 flex-1'>
          <p class='leading-relaxed text-base'>
            Domina el Local Pack de Google Maps y atrae clientes de tu zona. Optimización de Google Business Profile y estrategia de reputación para que tu negocio sea la primera opción.
          </p>
          <div class='flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-cream'>
            Ver servicio
            <ArrowRight class='size-4 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-1.5' aria-hidden='true' />
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>